OL,4,CCatholic Church 'cannot bless same-sex
OL,5,Cunions'
OL,6, The Catholic Church does not have the
OL,7, power to bless same-sex unions, the
OL,8, Vatican office responsible for doctrine
OL,9, has said.
OL,11,FIt is "impossible" for God to "bless
OL,12,Fsin", the Congregation for the Doctrine
OL,13,Fof the Faith (CDF) said on Monday.
OL,15,FBut the CDF did note the "positive
OL,16,Felements" in same-sex relationships.
OL,18,FIn October, Pope Francis said in a
OL,19,Fdocumentary that he thought same-sex
OL,20,Fcouples should be allowed to have
OL,21,F"civil unions".
